  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the beef and cook until browned, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the onion, carrots, celery, and garlic, and cook until the vegetables are tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the quinoa, beef broth, tomato paste, and diced tomatoes, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the stew to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Fluff the quinoa with a fork and season the stew with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs, if desired."
